org.linqs.psl.model.rule.arithmetic.expression

Interface SummationVariableOrTerm

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Term
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Attribute, Constant, DoubleAttribute, IntegerAttribute, LongAttribute, StringAttribute, SummationVariable, UniqueIntID, UniqueStringID, Variable

    public interface SummationVariableOrTerm
    Either a SummationVariable or Term. All implementing classes must be immutable. Hack for a union type (which is not directly supported in Java).
    Author:
    Stephen Bach
